# API Methods

## Search
```js
games.search(query);
```

## Filters
```js
games.filterSupported();
games.filterFavorites();
```

## Sorting
```js
games.sortBy('name');
games.sortByPopularity();
```

## Random
```js
games.random(3);
games.getRandomOne();
```

---

All methods (except `getRandomOne`) are **chainable**.

# Methods

## Connection
```js
peer.connect(id);
peer.close();
peer.destroy();
```

## Messaging
```js
peer.send(data);
```

## Media
```js
await peer.getStream();
```

---

## Static
```js
ZYNQ.peer.get(id);
ZYNQ.peer.destroyAll();
```
